{"tid":2032681,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"★ 再見忌廉哥】香港最紅貓店長忌廉哥逝世　今日4點與粉絲最後告別","createTime":"2020-05-24T07:44:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T12:14:33.000Z","uid":19454,"like":111,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"d1b28e4f9cce4a493b54ef8a94ff47e2ade81a5a","tid":2032681,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:44:31.000Z","msg":"已屆14歲高齡的忌廉哥今日已離世，其官方fb亦已證實消息。忌廉哥曾是尖東一間報檔的貓店長，憑其又肥又圓的可愛外表成功擄獲不少街坊歡心，紅透尖東一帶，及外更成為香港貓明星，紅遍中外網絡，更曾殺入CNN 電視台做訪問。官方fb表示，如粉絲想見忌廉哥，可以今日下午4:00前到忌廉家族。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2651449/【再見忌廉哥】香港最紅貓店長忌廉哥逝世%E3%80%80今日4點與粉絲最後告別\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2651449%2F%E3%80%90%E5%86%8D%E8%A6%8B%E5%BF%8C%E5%BB%89%E5%93%A5%E3%80%91%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%9C%80%E7%B4%85%E8%B2%93%E5%BA%97%E9%95%B7%E5%BF%8C%E5%BB%89%E5%93%A5%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96%25E3%2580%2580%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A54%E9%BB%9E%E8%88%87%E7%B2%89%E7%B5%B2%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E5%91%8A%E5%88%A5&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=6804a68f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2651449/【再見忌廉哥】香港最紅貓店長忌廉哥逝世%E3%80%80今日4點與粉絲最後告別</a>"},{"pid":"da8e833d7d7cc2b0041538fab13a4fa10308ac13","tid":2032681,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c51bea24a43d77adf4f8b30064e2408cbbd244ab","tid":2032681,"uid":90,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:45:03.000Z","msg":"老貓RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fro