屋企兩隻老過佢多多聲"},{"pid":"c789d6b76c61af901208388d99e3d090c8c4801d","tid":2032681,"uid":35107,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f35b506e98f14e22392c9751a44d1f5654b4d27c","tid":2032681,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:15:10.000Z","msg":"14歲唔係好老咋喎。。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:16:31.000Z","msg":"隻野咁撚肥<br />\n以前又鋪頭貓"},{"pid":"81ffccc9660a1032981137bf971d8454adfacce1","tid":2032681,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:16:43.000Z","msg":"RIP<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登紅色五毛分化警告</span><br />\n宜家班死五毛<span style=\"color: red;\">除左用鬥黃進行分化，仲用扮演移民/留守派黎進行分化</span>，大家請保持獨立思考<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後大家要幫手簽個聯署支持BNO平權救手足</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=13056f39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"0aeaca7e3dc047cb72f7802410da6e428bbf930b","tid":2032681,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c789d6b76c61af901208388d99e3d090c8c4801d","tid":2032681,"uid":35107,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f35b506e98f14e22392c9751a44d1f5654b4d27c","tid":2032681,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:15:10.000Z","msg":"14歲唔係好老咋喎。。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:16:31.000Z","msg":"隻野咁撚肥<br />\n以前又鋪頭貓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:17:44.000Z","msg":"唔同貓種唔同expected lifespan"},{"pid":"d4e745d23710fb77604241ccde12c76c950b6100","tid":2032681,"uid":35107,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0aeaca7e3dc047cb72f7802410da6e428bbf930b","tid":2032681,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c789d6b76c61af901208388d99e3d090c8c4801d","tid":2032681,"uid":35107,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f35b506e98f14e22392c9751a44d1f5654b4d27c","tid":2032681,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:15:10.000Z","msg":"14歲唔係好老咋喎。。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:16:31.000Z","msg":"隻野咁撚肥<br />\n以前又鋪頭貓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:17:44.000Z","msg":"唔同貓種唔同expected lifespan"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:18:23.000Z","msg":"佢係英短更短命"},{"pid":"d594faef66ff1b7b792817dfdfd5d1336fdf3e33","tid":2032681,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:19:34.000Z","msg":"rap"},{"pid":"7f49af7f5182aa4e4c13abf3141d031288019117","tid":2032681,"uid":149925,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f35b506e98f14e22392c9751a44d1f5654b4d27c","tid":2032681,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:15:10.000Z","msg":"14歲唔係好老咋喎。。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T08:19:35.000Z","msg":"用最多人知果種計法乘7都98歲"},{"pid":"585ef1a5ff6ca8042e8bdfce2ba3cf7da0727b9c","tid":2032681,"uid":82938